<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head xmlns:og="http://ogp.me/ns#">
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon" /> 
    <title><%=
      content_for?(:title) ? yield(:title) : "IAC Aerobatic Contest Data"
    %></title>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application" %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag "application", 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
    <%= yield :headers %>
    <script type='text/javascript'>
      $(function(){ $(document).foundation(); });
    </script>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <meta name="title" content="IAC Aerobatic Contest Data"/>
    <meta name="description" 
      content="Contest data and computed statistics for aerobatic contests
      of the International Aerobatic Club (IAC)"/>
    <meta property="og:title" content="IAC Aerobatic Contest Data"/>
    <meta property="og:type" content="website"/>
    <meta property="og:url" content="http://iaccdb.iac.org/"/>
    <meta property="og:image"
      content="http://iaccdb.iac.org/images/iac_logo_200.png"/>
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="IAC Contest Data"/>
    <meta property="og:description"
      content="Contest data and computed statistics for aerobatic contests
      of the International Aerobatic Club (IAC)"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="google-site-verification" content="eQl6GaBq3jeBLlrEB-P_EoeE78yAPDRAhtPfB7b1ypw" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="top-bar">
      <div class="top-bar-title">
        <span data-responsive-toggle="responsive-menu" data-hide-for="medium">
          <button class="menu-icon dark" type="button" data-toggle></button>
        </span>
        <strong><%= link_to "IAC CDB", root_path %></a></strong>
      </div>
      <div id="responsive-menu">
        <div class="top-bar-left">
          <ul class="dropdown menu" data-dropdown-menu>
            <li>
              <%= link_to 'Navigate', '#' %>
              <ul class='menu vertical'>
                <li><%= link_to 'Contests', contests_path %></li>
                <li><%= link_to 'Pilots', pilots_path %></li>
                <li><%= link_to 'Judges', judges_path %></li>
                <li><%= link_to 'Assistants', assistants_path %></li>
                <li><%= link_to 'Counts', further_participation_path %></li>
                <li><%= link_to 'Notes', pages_path(:notes) %></li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li><%= link_to 'Leaders', '#' %>
              <ul class='menu vertical'>
                <li><%= link_to 'Regional', leaders_recent_regionals_path %></li>
                <li><%= link_to 'Collegiate', leaders_recent_collegiate_path %></li>
                <li><%= link_to 'Soucy', leaders_recent_soucy_path %></li>
                <li><%= link_to 'Judges', leaders_recent_judges_path %></li>
              </ul>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="content">
      <p>Contact <a href="mailto:doug@wbreeze.com">Douglas Lovell</a> with questions and
         notice of any errors.
      </p>
      <div id='notice'><%= notice %></div>
      <div id='alert'><%= alert %></div>
      <%= yield %>
      <div id="footer">
        <p>Contact <a href="mailto:doug@wbreeze.com">Douglas Lovell</a> with questions and
         notice of any errors.</p>
        <p>As of the 2014 contest year, these are official results.
        Results prior to 2014 are computed by this system for study only.
        <p>See the
        <%= link_to 'Notes page', pages_path(:notes) %>
        for explanations of the numbers.</p>
        <p>These pages appear to you thanks to: </p>
        <ul>
          <li>"Manny," the contest results tracking system built by Randy Owens; </li>
          <li>"JaSPer," the contest scoring and data management system
          built by 'Bwana' Bob Buckley;</li>
          <li>Our contest scorekeepers who key-in the data; and</li>
          <li>Web wizardry by <a href="mailto:doug@wbreeze.com">Douglas Lovell</a></li>
        </ul>
        <p>Copyright &#169;2012-<%=Time.now.year%> Douglas Lovell</p>
        <p>Licensed under the
          <a href="http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0">
          Apache License, Version 2.0</a>
        </p>
        <p>Source hosted by
          <a href="https://github.com">GitHub</a> at
          <a href="https://github.com/wbreeze/iaccdb">github.com/wbreeze/iaccdb</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
